ent_alignment=\"\" pic_style_color=\"\" pic_bordersize=\"\" pic_bordercolor=\"\" pic_borderradius=\"\" icon_position=\"\" social_icon_boxed=\"\" social_icon_boxed_radius=\"\" social_icon_color_type=\"\" social_icon_colors=\"\" social_icon_boxed_colors=\"\" social_icon_tooltip=\"\" email=\"\" facebook=\"\" twitter=\"\" instagram=\"\" dribbble=\"\" google=\"\" linkedin=\"\" blogger=\"\" tumblr=\"\" reddit=\"\" yahoo=\"\" deviantart=\"\" vimeo=\"\" youtube=\"\" pinterest=\"\" rss=\"\" digg=\"\" flickr=\"\" forrst=\"\" myspace=\"\" skype=\"\" paypal=\"\" dropbox=\"\" soundcloud=\"\" vk=\"\" xing=\"\" show_custom=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/person][/one_half][one_half last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][person name=\"Sandra Stevens\" title=\"\" picture=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/1cff8db6e4eb2f73b9d3247d9ffe0bf6.jpeg\" pic_link=\"\" linktarget=\"_self\" pic_style=\"none\" hover_type=\"none\" background_color=\"\" content_alignment=\"\" pic_style_color=\"\" pic_bordersize=\"\" pic_bordercolor=\"\" pic_borderradius=\"\" icon_position=\"\" social_icon_boxed=\"\" social_icon_boxed_radius=\"\" social_icon_color_type=\"\" social_icon_colors=\"\" social_icon_boxed_colors=\"\" social_icon_tooltip=\"\" email=\"\" facebook=\"\" twitter=\"\" instagram=\"\" dribbble=\"\" google=\"\" linkedin=\"\" blogger=\"\" tumblr=\"\" reddit=\"\" yahoo=\"\" deviantart=\"\" vimeo=\"\" youtube=\"\" pinterest=\"\" rss=\"\" digg=\"\" flickr=\"\" forrst=\"\" myspace=\"\" skype=\"\" paypal=\"\" dropbox=\"\" soundcloud=\"\" vk=\"\" xing=\"\" show_custom=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/person][/one_half]\r\n\r\n[title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Always There, Exceptional Care[/title][fusion_text]Conveniently located in Turnersville, New Jersey, RegionalVet services the entire South Jersey and Philadelphia regions, including parts of Delaware.\r\n\r\nOur center, renowned for delivering exceptional and compassionate care, consists of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Emergency/Critical Care Center</li>\r\n 	<li>Specialty Services:\r\nCardiology\r\nDiagnosticImaging\r\nDermatology\r\nInternal Medicine\r\nSurgery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith specific patient care areas for Triage, Respiratory Therapy, Critical Care, Medical/Surgical Urgent Care, Radiology and Disease Control, the ER at RegionalVet is one of the regions finest.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Where would you turn if your pet required emergency,after-hours, or specialized medical treatment?</strong>[/title][fusion_text]For thousands of pet owners across the region, the answer is RegionalVet. Home to many of the area\'s top veterinary specialists, RegionalVet treats thousands of dogs and cats every year that have been referred to us by veterinarians who trust us to expertly care for their patients.[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\