solve diagnostic puzzles and treat severe and complex illnesses.\r\n\r\nRegionalVet Internal Medicine Doctors possess mastery of the following areas of study:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Endocrinology</li>\r\n 	<li>Gastroenterology</li>\r\n 	<li>Geriatric Medicine</li>\r\n 	<li>Hematology</li>\r\n 	<li>Infectious &amp; Immune Diseases</li>\r\n 	<li>Nephrology/Urology</li>\r\n 	<li>Pulmonology</li>\r\n 	<li>Rheumatology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]What Internists can help with[/title][fusion_text]<strong>Gastrointestinal Diseases</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Chronic Vomiting &amp;Diarrhea</li>\r\n 	<li>Endoscopic Diagnosis</li>\r\n 	<li>Liver and Kidney Disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Acute &amp; Chronic Hepatitis</li>\r\n 	<li>Acute &amp; Chronic KidneyFailure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Endocrine Disorders</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Difficult Diabetes</li>\r\n 	<li>Cushing\'s Disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Airway Disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Feline Asthma</li>\r\n 	<li>Chronic Cough</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Immune Disorders</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>IMHA (Immune Mediated Hemolytic Anemia)</li>\r\n 	<li>ITP (Immune Mediated Thrombocytopenia)</li>\r\n 	<li>Polyarthritis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Contact Us Now![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20482,12044,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20483,12045,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Cardiology at Regional Vet[/title][fusion_text]Veterinary cardiology, just like human cardiology, is a specialty in medicine that focuses on diseases that affect the heart and lungs. Congenital, valvular, pericardial, and myocardial (muscular) cardiac diseases are common among our pets and often go undetected until the disease is in advanced stages. Early and appropriate diagnosis and treatment of heart disease is essential for the best prognosis and quality of life for your pet.\r\n\r\nThe Cardiology Team at RegionalVetis trained to perform advanced non-invasive and minimally invasive diagnostics to evaluate your pet for underlying cardiovascular disease. Many cardiac diseases can be diagnosed with a simple non-invasive echocardiogram which uses ultrasound to view the structure and function of the heart.\r\n\r\nHowever, for more complex cardiovascular disease, advanced color flow Doppler, vascular contrast studies, nuclear cardiovascular medicine, and Holter Monitoring may be needed. RegionalVet performs each of those.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Diagnosed and treated atRegional Vet[/title][fusion_text]The following are heart conditions that we frequentlydiagnoseand treat:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Canine Valvular Disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Dilated Cardiomyopathy</li>\r\n 	<li>Hypertrophic Cardiomyopathy</li>\r\n 	<li>Congestive Heart Failure</li>\r\n 	<li>Congenital Heart Defects</li>\r\n 	<li>Sub-aortic Stenosis</li>\r\n 	<li>Pulmonary and Systemic Hypertension</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrhythmias (slow or fast)</li>\r\n 	<li>Arrhythmogenic Right Ventricular Cardiomyopathy (ARVC)</li>\r\n 	<li>Conduction Diseases</li>\r\n 	<li>Pericardial Diseases</li>\r\n 	<li>Feline Cardiomyopathies and Secondary Congestive Heart Failure (CHF)</li>\r\n 	<li>Feline Aortic Thromboembolic Events (FATE)</li>\r\n 	<li>Syncope</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Contact Us Now![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20484,12045,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20485,12043,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Surgery at Regional Vet[/title][fusion_text]Whether your pet requires a minimally invasive procedure or the most complicated life-saving intervention, the surgical team at RegionalVet can accommodate the needs of your companion. With our commitment to a standard of excellence you can expect integrity and compassion from our highly skilled surgical team lead by board certified specialists. All of our surgeons possess extensive surgical knowledge, superb clinical judgment, and advanced technical skills acquired over many years of education and experience.\r\n\r\nEach of our state-of-the-art, sterile surgical suites are comparable to the operating rooms in a human hospital. We have the safest anesthesia equipment in the industry. All surgical patients receive continuous readings of ECG, blood pressure, pulse oximetry, respiration and temperature monitoring during and after the anesthetic experience. In addition, endoscopy can be used before and during surgery to allow our doctors to visualize internal portions of your pet\'s body without making additional incisions. This can assist in both determining diagnoses, as well as ensuring your pet\'s procedure is as minimally invasive as possible.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]RegionalVet Surgical Specialists provide a full spectrum of surgical services including:[/title][fusion_text]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>General Soft Tissue Surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Abdominal Surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Thoracic Surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Wound Treatment</li>\r\n 	<li>Mass/Tumor Removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Orthopedic Surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Cruciate Ligament Surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Trauma surgery (fractures, ligament injuries)</li>\r\n 	<li>Congenital and developmental bone deformity treatment</li>\r\n 	<li>Patellar luxation</li>\r\n 	<li>Sports medicine</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Contact Us Now![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20486,12043,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20487,12042,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Radiology at Regional Vet[/title][fusion_text]The sooner a condition is diagnosed, the sooner healing can begin. Ultrasoundand Digital X-rays are some of the methods used by our doctors to find out what the best course of treatment is for your companion. With our leading-edge technology we can view crystal clear images on our flat-panel monitors anywhere in the hospital. We can enlarge scans and view different angles with the simple click of a mouse.\r\n\r\nOur attending doctors review every x-ray taken at RegionalVet, provide you right away with a preliminary reading and then submit the x-rays to a Board Certified Radiologist. All findings are then forwarded to your primary veterinarian. We will personally call you within 48 hours if there are changes to your pet\'s treatment plan as a result of the second review.\r\n\r\nResearch shows that abnormalities are missed in 30% of cases on radiographs (x-rays) seen by only one doctor. Your primary veterinarian may already be consulting with our radiology team to help review images taken at his or her facility.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Abdominal, Thoracic and Soft Tissue Ultrasound</li>\r\n 	<li>GI &amp; Vascular Contrast Studies</li>\r\n 	<li>Ultrasound Guided Biopsies and Aspirates</li>\r\n 	<li>X-ray Interpretation and Consults</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDiagnostic Imaging at RegionalVet is a vital resource for pet parents and veterinarians throughout South Jersey.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Need to view your radiographs?[/title][fusion_text]View your patient\'s radiographs on your PC, Tablet, Smartphone or iPad. Simply click the DVM Insight button below.\r\n\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"http://www.dvminsight.com/\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"#1e73be\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-share\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]DVM INSIGHT[/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20488,12042,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20489,12041,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Dermatology at Regional Vet[/title][fusion_text]The dermatology team at RegionalVet specializes in the diagnosis and treatment of dogs and cats with disorders of the skin, ears, hair, and nails. We know how frustrating these conditions can be for you and your treasured companion. Our skin experts aim to restore comfort and well-being using the latest techniques and highest standard of care.\r\n\r\nSkin conditions often require long-term monitoring to keep flare-ups at bay. Together with your primary veterinarian the dermatology team at RegionalVet will effectively implement a treatment protocol tailored for your pet.\r\n\r\nWhile RegionalVet does not currently have a Dermatologist in the office, we are completing refills for existing dermatology patients.\r\n\r\nBe sure to ask your primary veterinarian about the Dermatology Service at RegionalVet. Here are some of the conditions we treat:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bacterial skin infections (pyoderma)</li>\r\n 	<li>Yeast/fungal skin infections</li>\r\n 	<li>Food allergies</li>\r\n 	<li>Flea allergy dermatitis</li>\r\n 	<li>Environmental allergies (atopic dermatitis)</li>\r\n 	<li>Ectoparasitic diseases (fleas, ticks, mites and lice)</li>\r\n 	<li>Pododermatitis (disease of the foot)</li>\r\n 	<li>Auto-immune skin disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Endocrine/metabolic skin disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Drug reactions</li>\r\n 	<li>Chronic ear disease</li>\r\n 	<li>Skin cancer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<div id=\"wsb-element-384f9ab4-5149-42c9-b9ae-e403080813ef\" class=\"wsb-element-button\" data-type=\"element\"><strong>Testimonial</strong></div>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<div id=\"wsb-element-ed814bde-372c-420e-95b4-eb800e0f7adb\" class=\"wsb-element-facebook\" data-type=\"element\">Rocky\'s condition caused a slow decline in his health over a period of time. I had no idea how much it was affecting his quality of life. Once we started seeing Dr. Spiegel, Rocky\'s infection cleared right up and he finally stopped scratching.Now he\'s like a new cat!</div></blockquote>\r\n<div id=\"wsb-element-00000000-0000-0000-0000-000504798692\" class=\"wsb-element-text\" data-type=\"element\">\r\n<div class=\"txt \">\r\n\r\n- Valerie P.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/title][fusion_text]For thousands of pet owners across the region, the answer is RegionalVet. Home to many of the area\'s top veterinary specialists, RegionalVet treats thousands of dogs and cats every year that have been referred to us by veterinarians who trust us to expertly care for their patients.[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Contact Us Now![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20490,12041,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20491,12035,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][fusionslider name=\"final_full_screen\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/fusionslider][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Always There, Exceptional Care[/title][fusion_text]Conveniently located in Turnersville, New Jersey, RegionalVet services the entire South Jersey and Philadelphia regions, including parts of Delaware.\r\n\r\nOur center, renowned for delivering exceptional and compassionate care, consists of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>24/7 Emergency/Critical Care Center</li>\r\n 	<li>Specialty Services:\r\nCardiology\r\nDiagnosticImaging\r\nDermatology\r\nInternal Medicine\r\nSurgery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWith specific patient care areas for Triage, Respiratory Therapy, Critical Care, Medical/Surgical Urgent Care, Radiology and Disease Control, the ER at RegionalVet is one of the regions finest.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Where would you turn if your pet required emergency,after-hours, or specialized medical treatment?</strong>[/title][fusion_text]For thousands of pet owners across the region, the answer is RegionalVet. Home to many of the area\'s top veterinary specialists, RegionalVet treats thousands of dogs and cats every year that have been referred to us by veterinarians who trust us to expertly care for their patients.[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Contact Us Now![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20492,12035,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20493,11844,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text]\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 40px !important\">Need to reach us?</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: -20px\">RegionalVet has many [tooltip title=\"Flexible!\"]<b>appointments available</b>[/tooltip] so you can schedule within our hours listed below. If its an[tooltip title=\"Our ER is Open 24/7!\"]<strong>emergency</strong>[/tooltip] please just come right in!</p>\r\n[/fusion_text][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"25\" bottom_margin=\"25\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][two_third last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Contact Us</strong>[/title][fusion_text]Please call us at <strong>856-728-1400</strong> or submit your request below to schedule an appointment. Our Health Care Team looks forward to assisting you and your best friend.[/fusion_text][fusion_text][contact-form-7 id=\"6\" title=\"Contact Us Form\"][/fusion_text][/two_third][one_third last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>24/7 Emergency</strong>[/title][fusion_text]Our ER is open 24/7 to help take care of your pets when others can\'t.\r\n\r\nAlways there, exceptional care![/fusion_text][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Our Info</strong>[/title][fusion_text]\r\n<div class=\"heading\">\r\n<p class=\"widget-title\">4250 Route 42,</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"contact-info-container\">\r\n<p class=\"address\">Turnersville, NJ 08012</p>\r\n<p class=\"phone\">Phone: 888.830.8844</p>\r\n<p class=\"email\">Email: <a href=\"mailto:bestcare@regionalvet.com\">bestcare@regionalvet.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/fusion_text][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]<strong>Appointment Hours</strong>[/title][fusion_text]<b></b><b></b>Monday 9:00 am -8:00 pm\r\n\r\nTuesday9:00 am -8:00 pm\r\n\r\nWednesday 11:00 am -8:00pm\r\n\r\nThursday9:00 am -8:00 pm\r\n\r\nFriday9:00 am -8:00 pm\r\n\r\nSaturday9:00 am -3:00 pm\r\n\r\n[/fusion_text][/one_third]'),(20494,11844,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20495,11725,'fusion_builder_content_backup','[fusion_text][/fusion_text][fusionslider name=\"final_full_screen\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][/fusionslider][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"30\" bottom_margin=\"30\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][one_full last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"1\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #10086d\">Integrated Primary Care</span></strong></h1>\r\n[/title][fusion_text]Dogs and Cats can\'t make healthy choices for themselves. That\'s where we come in. Together we can keep your beloved companion as happy and healthy as can be. We take a modern, proactive approach to Veterinary Medicine focusing on Disease Prevention as a specific discipline. Our customized preventive plans are unique and effective in keeping illness at bay.\r\n\r\nOur Preventive Care patients enjoy the means of having all of their healthcare needs in one location. Similar to a modern pediatrician\'s office, the RegionalVet lobby is partitioned separating illness and emergency patients from well patients. However, we\'ve expanded on this model dedicating an entire wing of exam rooms to preventive care only. Our Preventive Care patients have access to all of our primary care, emergency and specialty physicians.[/fusion_text][/one_full][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h2><strong>Total Health Plan</strong></h2>\r\n[/title][two_third last=\"no\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][fusion_text]Congratulations! Perhaps you\'ve just adopted a new friend, or have raised your puppy or kitten successfully through the early stages of training and behavioral adaptation. Your adult pet has new considerations now, and proactive health management becomes more important than ever.\r\n\r\nThat\'s where the Health care Team at RegionalVet comes in. We\'ve simplified your adult pet\'s health with ourTotal Health Plan. Tailored around illness prevention and disease detection, the medical recommendations and protocols for health and preventive care are based on current medical science, years of evidence based wellness, illness and emergency clinical experience, and the belief that \"an ounce of prevention is worth a pound of cure\". With a focus on education and informed decision making, our Health Care Team is specifically selected and trained to understand the different life stages and health of your pet, as well as breed specific risk factors. We take a human approach to your pet\'s health, considering factors like proper nutrition, exercise, immunization and professional health screening. Dogs and cats age five to seven times faster than we do and diseases progress more quickly. For our best friends who can\'t tell us where it hurts, proactive health management makes common sense.\r\n\r\nIf you haven\'t done so already, call today to start aTotal Health Planfor your best friend![/fusion_text][/two_third][one_third last=\"yes\" spacing=\"yes\" center_content=\"no\" hide_on_mobile=\"no\" background_color=\"\" background_image=\"\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\" background_position=\"left top\" hover_type=\"none\" link=\"\" border_position=\"all\" border_size=\"0px\" border_color=\"\" border_style=\"\" padding=\"\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" animation_type=\"\" animation_direction=\"\" animation_speed=\"0.1\" animation_offset=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][flip_boxes columns=\"1\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][flip_box title_front=\"Keeping Your Pet Healthy\" title_back=\"Total Health Plan\" text_front=\"Our Total Health Plan considers your pet\'s specific breed, lifestyle and age and takes a proactive approach to the health your pet deserves. \" background_color_front=\"#10086d\" title_front_color=\"#ffffff\" text_front_color=\"#ffffff\" background_color_back=\"#fb660c\" title_back_color=\"#ffffff\" text_back_color=\"#ffffff\" border_size=\"1px\" border_color=\"\" border_radius=\"4px\" icon=\"fa-plus\" icon_color=\"#fb660c\" circle=\"yes\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" circle_border_color=\"\" icon_rotate=\"\" icon_spin=\"no\" image=\"\" image_width=\"35\" image_height=\"35\" animation_type=\"0\" animation_direction=\"down\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\"]With this innovative approach, the Total Health Plan provides optimal disease and illness prevention. Regardless of your pets age, breed or medical history there are five basic steps to the lifelong health of your pet:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Exercise</li>\r\n 	<li>Physical Examination</li>\r\n 	<li>Disease Prevention</li>\r\n 	<li>Wellness Diagnostics</li>\r\n 	<li>Nutrition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/flip_box][/flip_boxes][/one_third][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"10\" bottom_margin=\"10\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][button link=\"/regionalvet/contact-us\" color=\"blue\" size=\"xlarge\" stretch=\"\" type=\"flat\" shape=\"square\" target=\"_self\" title=\"\" gradient_colors=\"|\" gradient_hover_colors=\"|\" accent_color=\"\" accent_hover_color=\"\" bevel_color=\"\" border_width=\"\" icon=\"fa-check-circle-o\" icon_position=\"left\" icon_divider=\"yes\" modal=\"\" animation_type=\"slide\" animation_direction=\"left\" animation_speed=\"1\" animation_offset=\"\" alignment=\"center\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Schedule an Appointment![/button][separator style_type=\"none\" top_margin=\"20\" bottom_margin=\"20\" sep_color=\"\" border_size=\"\" icon=\"\" icon_circle=\"\" icon_circle_color=\"\" width=\"\" alignment=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][title size=\"2\" content_align=\"left\" style_type=\"double solid\" sep_color=\"#10086d\" margin_top=\"\" margin_bottom=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]Our Happy Clients[/title][images picture_size=\"fixed\" hover_type=\"none\" autoplay=\"yes\" columns=\"4\" column_spacing=\"13\" scroll_items=\"\" show_nav=\"yes\" mouse_scroll=\"no\" border=\"no\" lightbox=\"no\" class=\"\" id=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/12814016_1003637463048827_9176874882120683244_n-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/jazz-300x166.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/rocky.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][image link=\"#\" linktarget=\"_self\" image=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/mrs-peterson-300x215.jpeg\" alt=\"\"][/images]'),(20496,11725,'fusion_builder_converted','yes'),(20497,11726,'fusion_builder_content_backup','Regional Veterinary Emergency and Specialty Center is an integrated animal health system comprised of three centers of excellence:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>TotalHealth &am