 may fill out a RegionalVet Referral Form or call us to give details about the current diagnostics and treatments that you have already performed.\r\n\r\nWe can give you a rough estimate of costs that you can pass on to your clients before they arrive. Of course, individual costs will vary depending on the treatments required. Please let clients know that specific estimates can only be provided after consultation with an RegionalVet doctor.\r\n\r\nAccs a PDF referral form by <a href=\"http://dev.advertisingbros.com/regionalvet/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/referral-form.pdf\">referral-form</a>.\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/8FoeV3TcZfM'),(25834,12426,'pyre_wide_page_bg_color',''),(25835,12426,'pyre_wide_page_bg',''),(25833,12426,'pyre_page_bg_repeat','repeat'),(25832,12426,'pyre_page_bg_full','no'),(25830,12426,'pyre_page_bg_color',''),(25831,12426,'pyre_page_bg',''),(25829,12426,'pyre_page_bg_layout','default'),(25828,12426,'pyre_sidebar_bg_color',''),(25827,12426,'pyre_sidebar_position','default'),(25826,12426,'pyre_footer_100_width','default'),(25825,12426,'pyre_display_copyright','default'),(25824,12426,'pyre_display_footer','default'),(25823,12426,'pyre_displayed_menu','default'),(25822,12426,'pyre_header_bg_repeat','repeat'),(25821,12426,'pyre_header_bg_full','no'),(25819,12426,'pyre_header_bg_opacity',''),(25818,12426,'pyre_header_bg_color',''),(25816,12426,'pyre_display_header','yes'),(25814,12426,'pyre_hundredp_padding',''),(25813,12426,'pyre_main_bottom_padding',''),(25812,12426,'pyre_main_top_padding',''),(25809,12426,'pyre_avada_rev_styles','default'),(25810,12426,'pyre_fallback',''),(25807,12426,'pyre_elasticslider','0'),(25806,12426,'pyre_revslider','0'),(25805,12426,'pyre_wooslider','0'),(25804,12426,'pyre_slider','0'),(25803,12426,'pyre_slider_type','no'),(25800,12426,'sbg_selected_sidebar_replacement','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(25754,12426,'slide_template','default'),(25801,12426,'sbg_selected_sidebar_2','a:1:{i:0;s:1:\"0\";}'),(25799,12426,'sbg_selected_sideba